carts ->  total_price ,user_id -> 😎️👍️DOAA

cart_product -> product_id ,user_id, total_price(product_price * QTY) , QTY (default:1) ->😎️👍️DOAA

Orders -> id , total_price , employee_id(null) , dicount , tax(VAT 14%) , table_id , customer_id(null), payment_method ENUM('CASH','VISA') , (service_fee 12%), status ENUM('Pending',Accepted,'Prepare','Complete','Served','Canceled','Paid') -> sally

order_product -> order_id ,product_id ,  total_price , QTY (product_price * QTY)  , status Enum('complete',cancel)[null] ->sally


Tables -> number , guest_numbers,status enum('available','not available') [default:available] ->sally

Reservation -> start_date, end_date->nullable, table_id,customer_id,status ENUM('cancel','progress', 'completed','Accepted') -> sondos



